page.title: 11Hobbies and Interests
page.content: I am interested in World War 2 aircraft and I like making models of them.The sports I like are cricket football,snooker and judo.In judo I am a green belt and I am a member of the Esh Winning judo club. My main hobby is riding my friends horse called Samson.Isometimes go fishing with my dad.I like disco dancing. My interests are collecting posters of pop stars and drawing pictures I put them on my wall because they are more interesting than wallpaper. I like collecting matchboxes because my dad brings them back from holidays. I also like gymnastics,netball and riding my bike. I like collecting beermats,stamps and badges of different places I have visited.I enjoy making programmes on my computer.
